dc_description_s: This line shapefile represents the path of the Owens River from the Inyo/Mono County line south to the termination at Owens Dry Lake. These data were digitized from 2009 NAIP Imagery. in Inyo County, Califorina. This layer is a part of a collection of data obtained from Inyo County Information Services Department.
